2026-05-04T01:03:32.5521747Z 22    <!--
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5522475Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5523386Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5524231Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5525213Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5526201Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5527208Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5528143Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5529038Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5530170Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5531200Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5531808Z 33    -->
2026-05-04T01:03:32.5532473Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
